components.name: Fetch User Data
components.description: Retrieves user information from the external ReqRes API endpoint and pushes the JSON response to XCom.

components.name: Transform User Data
components.description: Parses the JSON user data from XCom, extracts firstname, lastname, and email, and pushes the processed fields to XCom.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after successful execution of fetch_user_data.

components.name: Create User Table
components.description: Executes a DDL statement to create the 'users' table in PostgreSQL with columns for firstname, lastname, and email.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after successful execution of transform_user_data.

connections.purpose: PostgreSQL database for storing user data

components.name: Insert User Data
components.description: Inserts the processed user fields into the PostgreSQL 'users' table using templated SQL with XCom values.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after successful creation of the users table and after transform_user_data provides processed fields.
